rows.label: soul25_P0101
rows.name:
Set us up for success!
Engage in close quarters!

rows.label: soul25_P0102
rows.name:
The opening move is ours!
Stagger 'em from up close!

rows.label: soul25_P0103
rows.name:
Close in on the enemy!
Take the advantage!

rows.label: soul25_P0201
rows.name: Lay down suppressive fire!

rows.label: soul25_P0202
rows.name:
Buff yourself if you wanna
survive this!

rows.label: soul25_P0203
rows.name:
Short term strategy!
Weaken them!

rows.label: soul25_P0301
rows.name:
Commencing engagement!
Rush the enemy position!

rows.label: soul25_P0302
rows.name: I'm moving in! Cover me!

rows.label: soul25_P0303
rows.name:
Our battle plan is sound.
Deploy auras on my mark!

rows.label: soul25_P0401
rows.name:
I have to slow their assault...
Requesting healing!

rows.label: soul25_P0402
rows.name:
I can still hold the line!
But I'll need support!

rows.label: soul25_P0403
rows.name:
It'll take more than this to
take me out! Give me a buff!

rows.label: soul25_P0501
rows.name:
I won't die here today...
Heal me, stat!

rows.label: soul25_P0502
rows.name:
This isn't where I fall...
Route healing to me!

rows.label: soul25_P0503
rows.name:
Give me a boost! I'll stop
'em, whatever the cost...

rows.label: soul25_P0601
rows.name:
Recommend...melee...
Urgh...

rows.label: soul25_P0602
rows.name:
Gwah... End it with...
a bullet to their heart...

rows.label: soul25_P0603
rows.name:
Watch your six...!
An aura will keep you safe...

rows.label: soul25_P0701
rows.name:
Get right in their grill! Hit 'em
once and make it good!

rows.label: soul25_P0702
rows.name:
That's how we do it!
Now for a bullet chaser!

rows.label: soul25_P0703
rows.name:
Critical hit! Make it count
extra with some debuffs!

rows.label: soul25_P0801
rows.name:
We've got an opening!
Get in and exploit it!

rows.label: soul25_P0802
rows.name:
Made it through!
A good shot'll put 'em down!

rows.label: soul25_P0803
rows.name:
I've got a good feeling!
Hit 'em with a debuff!

rows.label: soul25_P0901
rows.name:
They're begging for a bullet
in the gut! Do the honors?

rows.label: soul25_P0902
rows.name:
Don't let the size get to you!
Buff yourself, go for the kill!

rows.label: soul25_P0903
rows.name:
Leave nothing on the table.
Activate Overclock, now!

rows.label: soul25_P1001
rows.name:
Stop draggin' your heels!
Get in and get stabbing!

rows.label: soul25_P1002
rows.name: That's a hit! Fire, now!

rows.label: soul25_P1003
rows.name:
Tide of battle's turning!
Perfect time for a debuff!

rows.label: soul25_P1101
rows.name:
Watch me and keep up!
Crack open those auras!

rows.label: soul25_P1102
rows.name:
Is that all you're good for?
Dig deep, and use an aura!

rows.label: soul25_P1103
rows.name:
Shape up or you'll eat dirt!
Come on, put some effort in!

rows.label: soul25_P1201
rows.name:
Final push! Activating
Overclock, follow my lead!

rows.label: soul25_P1202
rows.name:
Think of nothing but offense!
Overclock, all the way!

rows.label: soul25_P1203
rows.name:
I'll start us off!
Get your auras ready.

rows.label: soul25_C0101
rows.name:
We're not stopping there!
I want you all over them!

rows.label: soul25_C0102
rows.name:
Don't lose your cool.
Suppressive fire, now!

rows.label: soul25_C0103
rows.name:
Heal up. There's more to
come before we can rest.

rows.label: soul25_C0201
rows.name:
They ain't hittin' us like
this... Get an aura in!

rows.label: soul25_C0202
rows.name:
Too slow!
Gimme a boost!

rows.label: soul25_C0203
rows.name:
That's my cue...
All guns! Concentrate fire!

rows.label: soul25_C0301
rows.name:
Can't miss this chance!
Give 'em no breathing room!

rows.label: soul25_C0302
rows.name:
Now we clinch it!
Make every bullet count!

rows.label: soul25_C0303
rows.name:
Don't leave me hanging!
Follow me into melee!

rows.label: soul25_C0401
rows.name:
Times like these call for
a timely buff!

rows.label: soul25_C0402
rows.name:
Stay sharp, or Mira'll chew
you up! Auras at the ready!

rows.label: soul25_C0403
rows.name:
Weaken the enemy! We're
ready to make the most of it!

rows.label: soul25_C0501
rows.name:
That's messed them up!
Take a second to buff!

rows.label: soul25_C0502
rows.name:
We're pulling ahead! Good
moment to get a buff in!

rows.label: soul25_C0503
rows.name:
Best foot forward!
Follow me into Overclock!

rows.label: soul25_C0601
rows.name:
Thanks!
Now give 'em hell in melee!

rows.label: soul25_C0602
rows.name:
Why, you shouldn't have.
Next step, shoot to kill!

rows.label: soul25_C0603
rows.name:
You've learned well. Give
yourself an aura for effort.

rows.label: soul25_C0701
rows.name:
Not bad at all. But we'll need
more strength than that still!

rows.label: soul25_C0702
rows.name:
Good looking out! But don't
forget to buff yourself too!

rows.label: soul25_C0703
rows.name:
Detail-oriented as always.
An aura should go down well!

rows.label: soul25_C0801
rows.name:
Don't let them get away!
Tie them up at close range!

rows.label: soul25_C0802
rows.name:
Don't be a negative Nancy!
Grace 'em with gunfire!

rows.label: soul25_C0803
rows.name:
Never give up, no surrender!
I'll need your support!

rows.label: soul25_C0901
rows.name:
We're in a good spot!
Keep stoking the fire!

rows.label: soul25_C0902
rows.name:
High ground secured! Time to
show off your marksmanship!

rows.label: soul25_C0903
rows.name:
This'll be a key position!
C'mon, don't stop shooting!

rows.label: soul25_C1001
rows.name:
Enemy hit the dust!
Better feed 'em some pain!

rows.label: soul25_C1002
rows.name:
Confirming target toppled!
Focus fire while they're down!

rows.label: soul25_C1003
rows.name:
A golden opportunity!
Hit home with a debuff, now!

rows.label: soul25_C1101
rows.name:
Enemy's been stunned!
Should be safe to pile in!

rows.label: soul25_C1102
rows.name:
Target temporarily immobile!
Swarm 'em!

rows.label: soul25_C1103
rows.name:
Enfeeble the enemy target
while they're staying put!

rows.label: soul25_C1201
rows.name:
Seize the opportunity!
The enemy needs a beating!

rows.label: soul25_C1202
rows.name:
Enemy's asleep!
Pump 'em full of lead!

rows.label: soul25_C1203
rows.name:
Get 'em from up close!
It's not cowardly, it's tactics.

rows.label: soul25_C1301
rows.name:
I'll hold 'em back!
You sock 'em hard!

rows.label: soul25_C1302
rows.name:
Target bound! Aim well,
then take your shot.

rows.label: soul25_C1303
rows.name:
Charge in! The enemy's
going nowhere.

rows.label: soul25_C1401
rows.name:
Taking fire! Damage noted.
Send healing, ASAP!

rows.label: soul25_C1402
rows.name:
Forget about me! Our foe
is the priority here, soldiers!

rows.label: soul25_C1403
rows.name:
I'm still five by five! All hands,
fire on the enemy position!

rows.label: soul25_C1501
rows.name:
Well, there goes my Doll...
I need healing, stat!

rows.label: soul25_C1502
rows.name:
They got me good!
Use a buff to turn it around!

rows.label: soul25_C1503
rows.name:
It's fine! You just get your
ass into Overclock!

rows.label: soul25_C1601
rows.name:
Push through!
A buff might help with that!

rows.label: soul25_C1602
rows.name:
My fuel reserves are out...
I need a top-up!

rows.label: soul25_C1603
rows.name:
I've got to refuel!
Holding the line is vital!
